ad_managed.description: Indicates this account belongs to a AD-managed user

admin.description: Indicates this account has local administrator privileges

last_login.description: A Unix timestamp showing the last time this user logged in

managed.description: Indicates this account belongs to a JumpCloud-managed user

real_user.description: Indicates this account represents an interactive user account vs. a system or daemon account

suspended.description: Indicates this account is suspended or locked out
